        <summary>What are the best apps for a 10-minute timer?</summary>
        <p>There are many great apps available, including built-in smartphone clocks, dedicated Pomodoro apps like Forest or Focus Booster, and web-based tools like the ones we discuss on our site.</p>
      </details>
    </section>
